Maintainer: The package maintainer <yg54@rice.edu>
Description: 
    This package is designed to fit and interpret Bayesian scalar-on-function regression (SOFR) models. The package implements methods introduced in the research paper "Bayesian adaptive and interpretable Scalar-On-Function Regression" (available at: https://arxiv.org/abs/2203.00784).
